{"tid":1656690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] HKDI cctv逐格睇","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T23:59:28.000Z","uid":294179,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca328eb2e40f061ca3324dbb7225f3848f0eab9","tid":1656690,"uid":294179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"圖片由lift_20191015.1700.mp4擷取<br />\ncctv時間:2019-09-19 17:50:39-17:51:58<br />\n地點: 香港專業教育學院(李惠利) [LW座] 11號升降機<br />\n圖片來源:立場新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87V6vdi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87V6vdi.png&h=ec43ed67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 陳同學於G層進入LW座11號升降機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjmA8e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjmA8e6.png&h=4c0f7781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳同學手持第一份文件 面頭文件大致為白色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDBQW8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDBQW8y.png&h=decf345a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片經後期處理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMaeEm6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMaeEm6.png&h=5cc90592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳同學左右手均戴有黑包幼手繩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SyQ2OfP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSyQ2OfP.png&h=8c1e9797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n升降機上升至M層<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPb13Pa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPb13Pa.png&h=dad4cae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n升降機上升至1樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ky7Znw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ky7Znw.png&h=cadcc226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n升降機上升至2?樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGif8fR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGif8fR.png&h=06cedcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n升降機上升至3?樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cvh41AS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvh41AS.png&h=2c76e5ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳同學觀看第二份文件，文件由黃色膠folder裝載兩份半A4 size 紙張組成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MmEQud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MmEQud.png&h=c9599b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlift門於3?樓開啟，一名中/老年男子進入 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzYjQud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzYjQud.png&h=ba1971af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該名男子上身穿著印有黑色橫條的白色T恤，下身穿著黑色長褲以及黑色白邊波鞋<br />\n該名男子左手穿戴黑色及深紅色手帶?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWPrvue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWPrvue.png&h=96dad596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子按lift 燈號在陳同學樓層的上一格亮起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzzSq2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzzSq2A.png&h=91bd0310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子以交差腳站立<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFmacHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFmacHA.png&h=a3407d59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳同學身上戴有紅色不知名物件以及疑似黑色證件套<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfSkzVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfSkzVW.png&h=15b7221c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳同學翻閱第二份文件 圖中所顯示為第二份文件底部<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JET0zVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJET0zVW.png&h=b3d84e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在第二份文件下是陳同學的電話(白色面)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVrJxHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVrJxHC.png&h=99f91fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykh41AX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fykh41AX.png&h=fbd6a167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電梯到達6?樓 陳同學離開6?樓 向DI方向離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fK0aW9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfK0aW9i.png&h=95f57985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子未有跟隨陳同學離開6?樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNN41AZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNN41AZ.png&h=aa16a0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電梯上升至6M層<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qoWSHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qoWSHF.png&h=2ee3be88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電梯到達7樓 男子離開電梯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RN37ZnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRN37ZnG.png&h=d20413c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子往DI方向離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qK3f8f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqK3f8f2.png&h=4d641690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我已找出cctv大部分細節，如有遺漏請及時指正<br />\n本帖以客觀描述cctv的畫面，請自行思考任何疑點</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後希望大家唔好忘記今個星期日民陣遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1SQcRH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1SQcRH.png&h=3cc23ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del></span></div>"},{"pid":"155eb71806584695a9b3dd0711edd544f5552885","tid":1656690,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"be482f449d379f4f0e08ae27102b93b63a97bef1","tid":1656690,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4x1jAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4x1jAD.jpg&h=425ca31a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c690dda900c52afd81e5ac45a381bf210e595eb","tid":1656690,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"多謝整理, 但現實D講句  ..段片放得出黎俾全世界睇 都唔會有咩證據可以睇到...(純粹想轉視線)"},{"pid":"ac33ce4d9d2aae88c9b7da7982f31410fe58aeb4","tid":1656690,"uid":317136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c690dda900c52afd81e5ac45a381bf210e595eb","tid":1656690,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"多謝整理, 但現實D講句  ..段片放得出黎俾全世界睇 都唔會有咩證據可以睇到...(純粹想轉視線)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得其實唔關嗰位中年阿伯事 好似你咁講 放得出嚟一定冇咩證據<br />\n但唔明白點解一開始放一半又唔放一半 所以先覺得可疑<br />\n雖然咁講好衰 但其實個女仔會唔會得罪咗啲咩人 所以俾人殺害 總之一定唔係自殺 一個女仔好好地咁...<br />\n希望可以搵到真相"},{"pid":"4d39799e1f8a7583040620f928bd93966688fef0","tid":1656690,"uid":214192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"其實段cctv證明唔到啲咩<br />\n成單case我地要focus嘅係<br />\n1. 佢啲行為完全唔似自殺嘅人會做嘅嘢，自殺前仲返學校拎返自己漏低嘅嘢/交功課？<br />\n2. 一個游泳健將點解會揀跳落海而自殺？<br />\n3. 佢自殺但係點解會係全裸？<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">警察根據啲咩ground嚟判斷佢係自殺而非他殺</span><br />\n班狗一定話佢哋睇過cctv認為係咁，但我見班狗好似係話睇hkdi嘅cctv佢向海濱方向走咋窩（有錯或有更新請指出）<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">根本係冇證據顯示霖霖係自殺，但警方一口斷定係自殺嘅意圖究竟係邊？係唔想查定包庇緊啲乜嘢</span>"},{"pid":"1b5ca2aa6c6b59284d0e34525aec4d6fc6199fc5","tid":1656690,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:28.000Z","msg":"點解你條片又會長左<br />\n大家流傳緊個條都係彥霖出左去𨋢門仲打開緊就完左<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e7w6t5lf8Oc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe7w6t5lf8Oc&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=373ec7f4\" data-